---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — BBQ It Guide & Tools" description="About the BBQ It Guide site. Learn about our tools, data sources, and mission to help BBQ It players.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About BBQ It Guide</h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What Is This Site?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">BBQ It Guide is an unofficial fan-made companion site for the Roblox game BBQ It. Our goal is to provide the most complete and useful collection of guides, calculators, codes, and tools for BBQ It players.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What We Offer</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li>• <strong>Complete guides</strong> — From beginner basics to advanced profit strategies</li>
        <li>• <strong>Working codes</strong> — Updated regularly from official sources</li>
        <li>• <strong>Meat tier list</strong> — All meats ranked by profitability</li>
        <li>• <strong>5 calculators</strong> — Profit, offline earnings, upgrade ROI, grill layout, and meat weight</li>
        <li>• <strong>Equipment guides</strong> — Grills, tables, smokers, and upgrades</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Data Sources</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Our game data comes from community observations, player reports, and in-game testing. All values are estimates and may not be exact. We verify and update our data after each major game update.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">This site is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Roblox Corporation or the BBQ It development team. BBQ It and Roblox are trademarks of their respective owners. This is a fan-created resource for informational purposes.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
